        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2012-2383">CVE-2012-2383</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2012-2384">CVE-2012-2384</a>
        

</p>





